<div id="pf43e4" class="pf w4f h303" data-page-no="43e4"><div class="pc pc43e4 w4f h303"><div class="t m1491 xd2 h49 y2f63 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 6 May 6-12 </div><div class="t m314 x71 h49 y23c8 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Behold, I come as a thief. Blessed </div><div class="t m1080 x15 h49 y1584 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is he that watcheth, and keepeth </div><div class="t m27f x15 h49 y15f2 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">his garments, lest he walk naked, and </div><div class="t mea8 x15 h49 ycce ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">they see his shame&quot; (Rev. 16:15). </div><div class="t m785 x26 h35 y3c9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">These inspired words apply to the </div><div class="t m418 x27 h35 y99d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">close of the investigative judgment </div><div class="t m171 x27 h35 ya41 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the period of grace. Both will </div><div class="t m8d9 x27 h35 y855 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">terminate at an unexpected time. To </div><div class="t m1480 x27 h35 y766 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this special moment the prophecy of </div><div class="t me66 x27 h35 y1289 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Daniel 12:1 also refers when it says, </div><div class="t mc3 x27 h35 yb0c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;There shall be a time of trouble, </div><div class="t m58f x27 h35 y1320 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">such as never was.&quot; Also Revelation </div><div class="t m8cb x27 h35 yb0d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">22:11 points to this specific hour, </div><div class="t m8cb x27 h35 yef5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">since when it comes, &quot;he that is </div><div class="t m59c x27 h35 ydf7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unjust&quot; continues to be unjust, and </div><div class="t m8f8 x27 h35 y720 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;he that is righteous&quot; continues to </div><div class="t m8b9 x27 h35 y821 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be righteous. </div><div class="t m828 x26 h35 y126b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The most important point about the </div><div class="t m22c x27 h35 yaac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">time of trouble is not to understand </div><div class="t me8d x27 h35 yc55 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">completely all the facts; but rather, </div><div class="t m6d2 x27 h35 yf89 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to have a firm, true faith in Jesus </div><div class="t ma6b x27 h35 y3a5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that will enable us to pass through </div><div class="t m6d2 x27 h35 y1256 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that ominous time safely. Those who </div><div class="t m1ab x27 h35 y843 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have a faith in Jesus that leads them </div><div class="t m6d x27 h35 y8d8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to obey Him will be protected fully </div><div class="t m5a1 x27 h35 y66 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">from the seven last plagues, sealed </div><div class="t m185 x11 h35 y8c0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by the seal of the living God for </div><div class="t mf4 x11 h35 y21b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eternal salvation and covered </div><div class="t m86 x11 h35 y12e7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">completely by the beautiful and </div><div class="t m70a x11 h35 y1131 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perfect garment of the righteousness </div><div class="t m33a x11 h35 y9c0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Christ. </div><div class="t m597 x18 h35 yc57 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The only key to victory is to have </div><div class="t maed x11 h35 y72d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a heart cleansed by the blood of </div><div class="t m8e x11 h35 y910 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus. This lesson seeks to confront </div><div class="t m7a6 x11 h35 y4f1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">us with our vital need of acquiring </div><div class="t m898 x11 h35 y7bf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the personal Christian experience of </div><div class="t m9b2 x11 h35 y674 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">one whose life &quot;is hid with Christ in </div><div class="t mb6e x11 h35 y78c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&quot; (Col. 3:3) so that nothing can </div><div class="t m7ce x11 h35 y1ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">affect him or change his glorious </div><div class="t m8d6 x11 h35 y122b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">destination. </div><div class="t m9b1 x4a h35 y344 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This is even more important in </div><div class="t m1ae x11 h35 yfbe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">view of the fact that the end of </div><div class="t m13c x11 h35 y6dc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">probation is very near, and it will come </div><div class="t m79d x11 h35 y153b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unexpectedly, even to the children of </div><div class="t mb47 x17 h35 y3b7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. </div><div class="t m38c x86 h49 y72e ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m12c x86 h49 y3ae ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m5c1 x9 h49 y3ae ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Seven Last Plagues </div><div class="t m316 xa5 h49 y37f ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Revelation 16) </div><div class="t m814 x86 h49 y7bf ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m559 xa5 h49 y11f0 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Protection and Care of God </div><div class="t m79a xa5 h49 y40f ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Ps. 91:1, 2, 15) </div><div class="t m66d x86 h49 y78c ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m62b xa5 h49 ycc5 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">No More Mediator: No More </div><div class="t ma20 xa5 h49 y803 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Probation (Rev. 15:8; 8:5) </div><div class="t m7e1 x86 h49 y8da ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m1083 xa5 h49 y5ab ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Unexpectedness of the Time </div><div class="t m8a4 xa5 h49 ya34 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 16:15) </div><div class="t m2ef x86 h49 yabf ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m5bb xa5 h49 yfbe ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Sealed </div><div class="t md0d xa5 h49 y6dc ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Eze. 14:20) </div><div class="t mb27 x86 h49 yc89 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t me72 xa5 h49 yc89 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Key to Success </div><div class="t m1377 xa5 h49 y3e7 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 